dbusiness to Standard Microsystems Corp., of Hauppauge, N.Y.andM;Standard, meanwhile, last week posted a $1.79 million loss for its firstfiscal quarter, ended May 31.andM;Company officials blamed the loss on caution in distribution channels aboutthe company's new Ethernet LAN card business and a slowdown in the PC market.andO;</TEXT></DOC>